     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<span class=\"tex2jax_ignore\"><div class=\"entities\" style=\"line-height: 2.5; direction: ltr\">Exploring \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Methamphetamine\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " Nonenantioselectively Targeting \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Toll-like Receptor 4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Myeloid Differentiation Protein 2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " by in Silico Simulations and Wet-Lab Techniques<br>\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Methamphetamine\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " (\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ") is one of the highly addictive nonopioid psychostimulants, acting as a xenobiotic-associated molecular pattern (XAMP) to target \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " and activate microglia. However, the molecule recognition of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " by innate immune receptor \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " is not well-understood. \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " exists in two enantiomeric forms, and it is unclear whether the \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " innate immune recognition with \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " is stereoselective. Herein, molecular dynamics (MDs) simulations were performed to dissect the recognition of (+)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " and (−)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " by \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " at the atomic level. \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Amphetamine\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " (\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    AMPH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "), which is an analogue of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ", was also investigated for comparison. Computational simulations indicate that \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " binds into the interaction interface between \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " as well as \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "* that is from the adjacent copy of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ", therefore stabilizing the active heterotetramer (\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ")2 complex. The calculated binding free energies and potential of mean force (PMF) values show that (−)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " and (+)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " have similar \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " binding affinity. Further dynamics analyses of bindings with \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " indicate that (−)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " and (+)-\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " behave similarly. Unlike the stereoselective neuron-stimulating activities of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ", no enantioselectivity was observed for \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " interacting with \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " complex as well as activating \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " signaling. Compared to \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ", \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    AMPH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " showed much weaker interactions with \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    MD-2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       ", indicating that the substituted methyl group is critical in the molecular recognition of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    METH\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " by \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TLR4\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       "/\n",
