      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_9788852.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/In-Cell_Protein_Protein_Contacts_Transient_Interactions_in_the_Crowd/9788852)\n",
