      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_3207154.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Accurate_Structure_Prediction_and_Conformational_Analysis_of_Cyclic_Peptides_with_Residue_Specific_Force_Fields/3207154)\n",
