       "<span class=\"tex2jax_ignore\"><div class=\"entities\" style=\"line-height: 2.5; direction: ltr\">Molecular dynamics trajectories of protein folding<br>Molecular dynamics trajectories of protein folding are deposited for educational purposes.<br>Currently, the following trajectories are available:<br><br>\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    Chignolin\n",
