       " in Pulmonary Surfactant Monolayers: Physical Properties Controlled by Specific Protein–Lipid Interactions. bioRxiv, pp.2022-12. (Pre-print available at https://doi.org/10.1101/2022.12.12.520108)<br> <br>\n",
