       " water model [2]. Each system consist of two monolayers with 169 lipids each. The monolayers are separated by a water slab, and surrounded by vacuum.<br>All trajectories are simulated for \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #baffc9; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
